flowRoot.flowPara: All pictures are then assigned to a keyword cluster. The cluster is chosen based on their title and tags, which have been cleansed previously. This allows to take into account in which context the searched term appears in the picture.
This is a subset of the result, depicting the "parrot" node. The vertical scale represents semantic groups, with subgroups obtained from the visual features where appropriate.
